<main class="container">

<div class="note"><strong>Quick answer:</strong> choose the <em>geographically closest</em> server with the <em>lowest ping</em> and <em>low load</em>. For specific tasks, use <em>Streaming</em>, <em>P2P</em>, <em>Obfuscated/Double VPN</em> or <em>Dedicated IP</em> profiles.</div>

